Use the standard library
This is how to get_odd_collatz of n:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that current is n
  Do this 1000 times:
    When current is 1, then:
      Add result to 1
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When remainder of current and 2 is 1, then:
      Add result to current
      Remember that current is sum of product of 3 and current and 1
    But, if not:
      Remember that current is quotient of current and 2
    End when
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know